1.Get all products
curl -X GET http://localhost:3000/api/products

2.Create a new product
curl -X POST -H "Content-Type: application/json" -H "x-api-key: YOUR_API_KEY" -d '{"name":"Smartphone","description":"Latest model","price":699.99,"category":"Electronics"}' http://localhost:3000/api/products

3.Get product statistics:
curl -X GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/stats
